    <item>
      <title>SED - AWK - Replace Section Within File</title>
      <link>http://jotschi.de/2009/10/10/sed-awk-replace-section-within-file/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Oct 2009 14:01:05 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://jotschi.de/2009/10/10/sed-awk-replace-section-within-file/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here is how to replace a multiline text between two tags or lines of text with awk or sed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;File: &#39;test&#39;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;listingblock&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;###START
1
2
###STOP&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sect1&#34;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;_sed&#34;&gt;SED:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sectionbody&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sed  -i -e &#34;/&lt;sup&gt;&lt;mark&gt;START\$/,/&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/mark&gt;STOP\$/c &lt;mark&gt;START\n${REPLACEMENT}\n&lt;/mark&gt;STOP&#34; test&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;listingblock&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;AWK:&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;awk &#34;/&lt;mark&gt;START/{p=1;print\&#34;&lt;/mark&gt;#START\n${REPLACEMENT}\n&lt;mark&gt;#STOP\&#34;;next}/&lt;/mark&gt;STOP/{p=0;next}!p&#34; test.tmp &amp;gt; test&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;listingblock&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Note: test must be copied to test.tmp before replacement can be done.&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
